{"tid":1206520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(出現了)開始見到好多acc上水，叫人唔好衝，散水","createTime":"2019-06-12T03:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T10:29:00.000Z","uid":190928,"like":208,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"b1fc623b705adc4cfb63a16c884450aa47ae17a0","tid":1206520,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請廣傳<br />\n銘記五年前嘅慘痛教訓<br />\n唔可以今日唔開大會 就收貨<br />\n亦絕對唔可以同鬥長命 <span style=\"color: red;\">久守必失</span><br />\n唔要階段性勝利 唔要俾啲掌聲自己 只係要贏！<br />\n就係今日 迫政府撤回修例！<br />\n<br />\n不撤 不退！不散！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"99804dfb3e82e21e10391cc1cf0d8c94832b384d","tid":1206520,"uid":190928,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推推，唔好只係正評"},{"pid":"8ab2541b90bd3fe3a153bac714954462bcbecc43","tid":1206520,"uid":84511,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"一定要繼續攻入立法會<br />\n撤回係今次行動嘅基本要求<br />\n不斷同警察對抗 打擊佢地士氣<br />\n比壓力佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家日光日白大把cam影住 佢地唔敢做嘢<br />\n我地不斷同佢地對抗<br />\n政府一低頭一撤回成班警察就做哂傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察質疑政府以後香港人示威就好辦事"},{"pid":"24f7691e743fc2635c41101826af27572ae96ad7","tid":1206520,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1a63cb136a50834b4d53efe16a36f4c856144b","tid":1206520,"uid":179283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"無錯 今日唔衝又等無人先衝?"},{"pid":"61dee2253a04ba2a39a6395eaf77cd4d170fd46a","tid":1206520,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"一係佔領立法會，咁係近乎政變，一係用外圍因素對賭"},{"pid":"23cb6ad036b2b5538d9b26b17940815e8e290cfd","tid":1206520,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61dee2253a04ba2a39a6395eaf77cd4d170fd46a","tid":1206520,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"一係佔領立法會，咁係近乎政變，一係用外圍因素對賭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"【用腦諗下】 建制議員帶頭撤資，只係開始<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1206529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1206529</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地有嘅係時間，如果個勢唔變就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n但係要點變個勢先會返嚟我哋呢邊？等佢哋變返轉頭？唔可能係衝，一定係一啲利益關係，而家要做嘅係加大注碼，攞返個主導權，時間要改為由我哋定，唔可以我哋急佢哋唔急<br />\n<br />\n打係不智，日頭可能得到冇好處嘅小勝利，但係在場嘅人總會有個時間走緊大部分，又會一啲死守，而天總會黑，今晚未必可以好似尋晚咁，如果搞唔好，可能要損失<br />\n<br />\n要打擊士氣，但係唔係打擊警方士氣，而係打擊政府同建制士氣<br />\n<br />\n建制議員帶頭撤資，只係開始，你要諗吓，建制支持政府係要有利益，冇利益邊個做，一方面睇，建制賣嘢係減風險，好似係支持滅港走定先，但另一方面，其實變現走資係令其本身更接近自由身，反而未必一定要支持政府"},{"pid":"3e9390029eb368564e8000da7d8bf1c8add5cc2d","tid":1206520,"uid":8265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ebb77196098d92def5246a3957e3e5dc9f70da1","tid":1206520,"uid":134088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"不撤不退<br />\n<br />\n要贏!"},{"pid":"53a9c2c69d4dfa0775a1ec9a2e61c8500b8fb815","tid":1206520,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:00.000Z","msg":"必須衝 唔衝唔通等運到 同時一定要小心"},{"pid":"1aacef50c3a0d738895f83625dc5ec093c0af2aa","tid":1206520,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>不撤不退<br />\n<br />\n要贏!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8ceee9bf4150f7a3d7ed52269ff2934260f28e24","tid":1206520,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"支持  不散<br />\n直到撤回"},{"pid":"eefde5bc457c23dd0d4d8b5acb5c6e0a6f1bea4f","tid":1206520,"uid":32749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d8e87206439d9d98a4ed1c86d847ec39b2627642","tid":1206520,"uid":17042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01509c94c362251c009bff2155ebbb91a447c6e6","tid":1206520,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abb1ca77bbbe73889f69e343be7d119f776e4bb9","tid":1206520,"uid":37990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2aa0f9e41f2d53e09db32c8f96008da0933dee8","tid":1206520,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"特別留意大台post, 太明顯<br />\n尋晚連登個個咁有士氣，今朝咁左膠，唔正常<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對唔好俾雨傘重演，2014係個俾左膠玩死嘅失敗運動</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"25ade5d42317a0daa062c31419987f20e2db8bb0","tid":1206520,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"aa4d048852d225424921c08522e28f61b3b3b57e","tid":1206520,"uid":58188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c544fb054e8ff3feb702190d7266bdddf171b0f","tid":1206520,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"話比身邊人知拖越耐越不利<br />\n示威者都會累<br />\n政府會有更多時間計劃同操作各方面牽制示威<br />\n絕不能比政府拖延<br />\n要設時限升級施壓，保持令國際新聞關注<br />\n香港輸左就玩完<br />\n絕對唔可以讓步/階段性勝利<br />\n目標只有「撤回」<br />\n今次唔贏以後我地示威抗爭政府都唔會再怕！<br />\n警察同政府而家係重複緊雨傘時既戰略<br />\n香港人要開始轉變<br />\n和理非+適當既勇武配合我地先有一線機會<br />\n雨傘衰過一次<br />\n預演又錯過一次時機<br />\n唔好再重複犯錯，會斷送成個香港後悔一世<br />\n加油呀香港人！"},{"pid":"9aca8eebfecb3a22af9521810e05565a8d621bd1","tid":1206520,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3a3b3bdcbddf56b025d5d10570d5095195aa738","tid":1206520,"uid":259015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0