ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89a24e46ec4e75500dec0e9d494475b505a7f75","tid":1206520,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bcc66d292c62cc8229af0db36926b42b61fcf4af","tid":1206520,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28efd89b0b444f567f2e58e2338b2a40c0ad6a0a","tid":1206520,"uid":190928,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bcc66d292c62cc8229af0db36926b42b61fcf4af","tid":1206520,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察已開槍，你已經無得揀，Do or die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開始見到好多acc上水，叫人唔好衝，<span style=\"color: red;\">邊個掟磚就係暴徒就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n銘記五年前嘅慘痛教訓<br />\n唔可以今日唔開大會 就收貨<br />\n亦絕對唔可以同佢鬥長命 <span style=\"color: red;\">久守必失</span><br />\n唔要階段性勝利 唔要俾啲掌聲自己 只係要贏！<br />\n就係今日 迫政府撤回修例！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不撤退！不留守！入立法會！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔好俾雨傘重演</span>，咪忘記2014係個俾左膠玩死嘅失敗運動</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4cdc5920d9728277e209eea3c09b1f031ff0facc","tid":1206520,"uid":180127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b384cd1b6670bbde9c0b08519b628ad430a2249","tid":1206520,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c65b316b6f97fdaefd85dcbe749d0472a7a021","tid":1206520,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>請廣傳</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫你克制冷靜，行動降級嘅人，同政府口徑一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n論係TG定連登，尋晚開始一大堆acc突然湧出嚟，叫人散，叫人降級，好多巴打信咗佢哋中晒伏。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請唔俾佢哋迷惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n佢哋嘅目的就係要係後線 (連登，各大TG group) 亂人心，令你軟弱，減輕前線(警察防線)嘅工作壓力，最後令你哋被瓦解。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋最常用嘅手段，係恐嚇</span>，例如：<br />\n1. 收到風，X點準備用實彈，走呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. X點鐘清場，會出實彈，返屋企啦求吓你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 班狗打到癲咗，走啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 唔好掟乜掟物，一陣間人哋有藉口升級武力，要醒少少，和平示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 暴動罪坐好多年架，唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請記住以上說話全部同政府，警察利益一致。</span>就係想你弱，想你怯，想你散。你手段越弱，警察就越唔洗用啲係鏡頭前睇落核突嘅手段招呼你，減輕輿論壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">你越弱，佢越輕鬆</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面對呢啲言論，可以試吓咁諗：<br />\n和理非？2014年雨傘佔足三個月，大前日百萬行，結果呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好升級？尋日無升級，咪一樣開槍打頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再搞入暴動？而家777已經定性咗係暴動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7738475922039214755bcd18c8aafecdda4633fa","tid":1206520,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4f28f292cf45009a37a3d9bb2f1caaceee8d109","tid":1206520,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:41:13.000Z","msg":"同雨革10.01時一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"對家想拖，點睇"}]}